Class Summary
AppProps Class AppProps is a fluent helper for setting various application level properties that every Flow may or may not be required to have set.
ConfigDef The ConfigDef class allows for the creation of a configuration properties template to be applied to an existing properties configuration set.
PropertyUtil Class PropertyUtil is a static helper class for handling properties.
Props Class Props is the base class for frameworks specific properties helper classes.
UnitOfWorkDef<T> Class UnitOfWorkDef is the base class for framework specific fluent definition interfaces.
